The differential test harness in this repository links against Drools
9.44.0.Final (retrieved from Maven Central) at test time only; Drools is not
distributed with, embedded in, or required by the Seine engine crate.

The scenarios under scenarios/baseline/ are adapted from test cases in the
Drools 9.44.0.Final regression suite (drools-test-coverage module,
https://github.com/apache/incubator-kie-drools, Apache License 2.0,
Copyright Red Hat, Inc. and/or its affiliates, and the KIE community).
Each scenario records its upstream source file and test method in a
"provenance" field, together with the adaptations applied (DRL rule text
adapted to declared scalar types; test-harness statements translated to
scenario facts). These adaptations are derivative works of the upstream
test content and are used under the Apache License 2.0.
